<!doctype html>
%html
  %head
    %meta(charset="utf-8")
    %title Scatter.FM | Last.FM Visualisation
    %link(href="lib/bootstrap/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet")
    %link(href="style.css" rel="stylesheet")
  %body
    .topbar
      .topbar-inner
        .container-fluid
          %a.brand(href="/") Scatter.FM
          %ul.nav
            %li
              %a About
    #intro_page.container
      .hero-unit
        :markdown
          # Your Life Soundtrack

          We associate music with our memories. 
          
          Recall the music of your past, and unlock old memories.

          See your entire listening history... in one graph.
        %form#userForm
          %input#userInput(name="user" placeholder="Last.FM Username")
          %input.btn.primary(type="submit" value="Visualise my scrobbles!")
      .span5
        :markdown
          ## Your listening story
          Life changes often precipitate changes in listening
          habits - your listening history can give insight into
          your life history.

          Is your story reflected in your songs?
      .span5
        :markdown
          ## When did I listen to...
          - **Sgt. Pepper's Lonely Hearts Club Band** for the first time?
          - **Party Rock Anthem** on repeat for three hours straight?
          - My favorite artists for the first time?
      .span5
        :markdown
          ## What did I listen to...
          - two years ago?
          - at Tyler's party?
          - at work last summer?
          - out at the beach at Christmas?
    %script(src="lib/jquery.min.js")
    %script(src="index.js")
    %script(src="http://static.getclicky.com/js")
    :javascript
      clicky.init(236155);
    %noscript
      %p
        %img(alt="Clicky" height="1" src="http://in.getclicky.com/236155ns.gif" width="1")
